Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.35,0:22:53.85,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}光も闇もないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.02,0:22:58.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}表も裏でも君だよ
